Product description

BE SAVAGE Solid Sherpa Oversized Jacket, designed for those who embrace both comfort and style. This jacket combines the soft, plush feel of Sherpa fabric with a contemporary oversized silhouette, making it a must-have for any fashion-forward individual. Perfect for layering, this versatile piece can be worn on chilly evenings, casual outings, or as part of a cozy loungewear ensemble.

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.
